snippet.title: MLB The Show 23 - Game Sizzle Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/mlb-the-show/

Get a first look at MLB The Show 23 gameplay on PlayStation 5. 
MLB The Show 23 is available March 28, 2023 on PlayStation 5 and PlayStation 4. Get Early Access beginning March 24, 2023 with The Captain Edition or Digital Deluxe Edition.
